tried to save him?

394
00:33:11,974 --> 00:33:13,235
There's a wound.

395
00:33:13,335 --> 00:33:14,514
He was killed.

396
00:33:16,375 --> 00:33:17,834
I touch something.

397
00:33:34,415 --> 00:33:35,395
Give it to me.

398
00:33:44,254 --> 00:33:46,074
It's the Zhang family's qilin emblem.

399
00:33:46,494 --> 00:33:48,915
Does this mean that
someone from our family

400
00:33:49,054 --> 00:33:50,773
once entered Zhang Family Castle

401
00:33:50,774 --> 00:33:52,675
and got sealed inside?

402
00:33:55,254 --> 00:33:56,395
Care no more.

403
00:33:56,454 --> 00:33:57,533
Let's break down this wall.

404
00:33:57,534 --> 00:33:58,733
We'll see

405
00:33:58,734 --> 00:34:00,435
what's going on.

406
00:34:32,454 --> 00:34:34,195
Why is there only half of it?

407
00:34:37,654 --> 00:34:38,794
Four.

408
00:34:40,174 --> 00:34:41,394
Mr. Yu.

409
00:34:42,174 --> 00:34:43,653
Come, have a seat.

410
00:34:43,654 --> 00:34:44,715
Alright.

411
00:34:46,094 --> 00:34:47,155
Thanks.

412
00:34:48,494 --> 00:34:49,635
Mr. Yu.

413
00:34:49,935 --> 00:34:51,834
The data I own is incomplete.

414
00:34:52,054 --> 00:34:53,235
I know.

415
00:34:53,415 --> 00:34:55,013
No, I mean,

416
00:34:55,014 --> 00:34:56,694
is there any other data?

417
00:34:56,695 --> 00:34:57,294
Yes.

418
00:34:57,295 --> 00:34:58,954
Could you show it to me?

419
00:35:00,614 --> 00:35:01,334
Mr. Yu?

420
00:35:01,335 --> 00:35:02,394
Yes?

421
00:35:03,335 --> 00:35:04,555
I mean...

422
00:35:04,974 --> 00:35:05,613
The data.

423
00:35:05,614 --> 00:35:06,595
Oh.

424
00:35:07,735 --> 00:35:08,995
The data

425
00:35:09,255 --> 00:35:10,515
