426
00:35:11,134 --> 00:35:12,613
I'll look for it.

427
00:35:12,614 --> 00:35:14,493
Once I find it,
I'll hand it over to you.

428
00:35:14,494 --> 00:35:16,555
Okay, thank you.

429
00:35:17,094 --> 00:35:18,274
And also this.

430
00:35:19,255 --> 00:35:20,474
Regarding these paintings,

431
00:35:20,534 --> 00:35:21,995
